  "text": "A recent publication deals with the detection of aflatoxin B1 by using an immunosensor [CITATION_1] . AuNPs of different size and origin were immobilized on the sensor surface, in order to increase the work surface and then enhance the signal. The developed method was compared with HPLC reference measurements with good results and then used in the detection of aflatoxin in paprika matrix.",
